    {
      "_id": "ad381d482b0023c2",
      "name": "NPC’s on Death’s Door",
      "sort": 8,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"2be1b90a-e081-80ca-a35e-f835ecfca46a\" class=\"block-color-default\">Monsters and NPCs normally die when they’re reduced to 0 HP, however the Game Master can choose to implement Death’s Door on special enemies. They would drop down to <strong>1 A</strong>P and be on Death’s Door in that same weakened state, leaving a window for them to still talk to the party and get out any last words before someone puts them out of their misery.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
